listing_description: A stylish modern duplex apartment house located in the centre of Sylhet town. The apartment comes with its own private parking and caretaker. It is a very minimalist and stylish apartment with a very fresh look and feel. Its is very spacious and has plenty of light throughout the house due to very large windows. It has 3 ensuite master bedrooms and 1 shared bathroom and toilet. It has a very spacious living and dining room area and remains very cool throughout the year due to it's openness!
